text: Different Fortunes () is a 1956 Soviet drama movie directed by Leonid Lukov.РАЗНЫЕ СУДЬБЫТатьяна Пилецкая представила в Петербурге фильм о балете, где исполнила главную роль It stars Tatyana Piletskaya, Yulian Panich, and Georgi Yumatov. == Actors == * Tatyana Piletskaya as Tanya Ogneva * Yulian Panich as Fedya Morozov * Georgi Yumatov as Styopa Ogurtsov * Tatyana Konyukhova as Sonya Orlova * Valentina Ushakova as Vera Zubova == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1956 drama movies Category:Soviet drama movies Category:Movies directed by Leonid Lukov
title: Different Fortunes
